COMPILING AND RUNNING
=====================

 There should be instructions for compiling and running MPQC where you got
the source distribution.  If not, the documentation can be made changing
directory to "src/bin/mpqc/doc" and typing "make mpqc.dvi", "make mpqc.ps",
or "make mpqc.html", as you please.  These commands might not complete
depending on your system's setup.  In this case you will be stuck reading
the TeX source files.
